On August 23 2017, Apax funds [announced their acquisition](https://www.thoughtworks.com/news/apax) of ThoughtWorks, Inc. As you all know, GoCD is supported by ThoughtWorks with our core team members being ThoughtWorks employees. We wanted to share what this news means to the GoCD product, its contributors, and the open source community. 

If you'd like to read more about the acquisition, [this post by Martin Fowler](https://martinfowler.com/articles/201708-tw-sale.html) has interesting context about the news.

## The impact on GoCD

For the GoCD core team there will be no change. ThoughtWorks is committed to building the best open source continuous delivery tool there is. We will continue to innovate by building on thought leadership and feedback from this community. 

In fact, now seems like a great time to share what's coming next with GoCD.

